    The class Road that can represent the edges of a Graph of Towns. The class must implement Comparable. The class stores references to the two vertices(Town endpoints), the distance between vertices, and a name, and the traditional methods (constructors, getters/setters, toString, etc.), and a compareTo, which compares two Road objects.
